snippet.title: SULFUR Teaser Trailer 2023
snippet.description:
Ocean screaming,
Twisting, turning
Mouth is dry,
Eyes are burning

Live page now on Steam! Wishlist and we'll be forever grateful! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2124120/SULFUR/   

Discord: https://discord.com/invite/TZtTYCcZex
Twitter: https://twitter.com/perfectrandom_
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/SulfurGame/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/sulfurgame

SULFUR is a modern old-school action-adventure: Outsmart enemies, find treasure, improve weapons, harness powers. Delve deeper, find answers, make it end.
